Official CKIP CoreNLP Toolkits
------------------------------

Features
^^^^^^^^

- Sentence Segmentation
- Word Segmentation
- Part-of-Speech Tagging
- Named-Entity Recognition
- Sentence Parsing
- Co-Reference Resolution

